snippet.title: Ruby Rose ~ Ace Attorney Profiles - Ruby
snippet.description:
THIS IS NOW A PLAYABLE GAME - http://aceattorney.sparklin.org/V6_Test/player.html?trial_id=63621

------------

This video is pretty much a progress report on Ruby Rose Ace Attorney.

60% of Ruby sprites are now completed. The script is also complete for the case. I'll be making more of these videos as I complete the sprites for the other characters.

---
More Ruby Rose Ace Attorney here - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLM9lVP5_rVu27Qj5eUKHeLh6e_iizvGSJ

Ruby Rose Ace Attorney is (will be) a crossover between the Ace Attorney series and the RWBY webseries.
